'''''Venom Brews, Immortality Looms''''' is an [[Adventure Mission]] on [[The Xianzhou Luofu]].

==Steps==
# Go to the Realm-Keeping Commission Chancery
# Listen to Qingzu's assignment
# Look for the suspicious people at Exalting Sanctum
# Copy the ''Thousand-Handed Merciful Medicus' Salvation'' 0/500 times
# Copy the ''Thousand-Handed Merciful Medicus' Salvation'' 1/500 times
# Copy the ''Thousand-Handed Merciful Medicus' Salvation'' 2/500 times
# Give your transcribed scripture to Green Hibiscus
# Copy the ''Thousand-Handed Merciful Medicus' Salvation'' 3/500 times
# Give your transcribed scripture to Green Hibiscus
# Copy the ''Thousand-Handed Merciful Medicus' Salvation'' 4/500 times
# "Battle" with the strange Cloud Knight
# Wait for further contact from Qingzu
# Meet up with Green Hibiscus at the Exalting Sanctum
# Go to the Exalting Sanctum and intercept the parcel according to the instruction of the missive
# Meet with the Disciples of Sanctus Medicus' person in charge of the Exalting Sanctum chapter
# Head to the Seat of Divine Foresight and report to Qingzu
# Head to the Exalting Sanctum and ask around for Draught of Draconic Surge's recipe
# Talk to Dan Shu

